Cell.Text: [S] S|We're all trying to become better mages, right? | Well, I need someone I can practice a few spells on. Nothing dangerous, really. Would you be willing to assist me?
I still need someone to practice a few spells on. Interested?

Node.Caption: MGRAppBrelyna01InitialBranchTopic: What do you need help with?

Cell.Text: Well, I... I simply thought you might wish to help out one of your fellow mages. | If that's not enough, I suppose... I have this amulet you could take.
No, not that kind of spell. Believe me when I say I wouldn't be asking if it weren't necessary.
[S] Oh, good. I was afraid I'd have to go ask J'zargo. | Now, you just stand there...
[S] Oh, good. I was afraid I'd have to rely on Onmund. | Now, you just stand there...
[S] Thank you. I was afraid I'd have to figure out some way to do this on my own. | Now, you just stand there...
Oh. Well, if you change your mind, let me know.
[S] It's not! | It shouldn't be. You'll be back to normal in no time. | And when you are, we can try this again and I'll be sure to get it right.
I am so very sorry. I went over this again and again, and I was sure it would have better results.

[S] I'm not really sure. I think it's just a minor miscalculation on my part. | I'm sure it will wear off soon. When it does, you'll be perfectly fine, and then we can try again. | In the meantime, I'll see about figuring out what went wrong.
Exactly as I said it would. | Now, are you ready to try again? I am confident it will work this time.
[S] Good, good. It'll be worth it, I assure you.
Well I really would like to make sure I've corrected what happened last time. | Please give me a chance to try again.
Well, it all worked out in the end, didn't it?
[S] Agreed. | And thank you for your help. You're a good friend.

Node.Caption: MGRAppBrelyna01FinalResponse1: Let's never speak of this again.

Cell.Text: [S] Oh, no it hasn't. Let's be honest. | I have a long way to go before I'm ready for the kind of advanced magic I've been attempting. | But at least I know where to start now. Thank you, you've been a great help to me.
